{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2337125, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同问", "timestamp": 1629656929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果感觉自己很抑郁 先去看医生！！！", "timestamp": 1629657024, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2337127, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: Alice已经看了一年多医生，吃了一年多药了，还是找不到活下去的理由...", "timestamp": 1629657422, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337133, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉自己活着完全是由于惯性...", "timestamp": 1629657442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2337132, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我已经看了好几年医生，吃了好几年药了，也找不到", "timestamp": 1629657479, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "今年因为感情抑郁症复发了，现在每天疼的起不来，躯体化反应...之前已经好了戒掉药了结果栽了个新坑，最近每天发抖喘不上气，一直哭，真的找不到啥理由了", "timestamp": 1629657532, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337140, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2337138, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那就再去看病吃药，感觉之前好过已经很棒了，一定可以再好的！", "timestamp": 1629657958, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2337305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "patpat dz，现在找不到活下去的理由很可能是抑郁导致看什么都带了层灰色，可这不代表未来找不到；而且如果现在就选择结束就真的永远找不到了", "timestamp": 1629678668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2338431, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2337132, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 吃药+心理咨询～ 另外每天得适当运动，如果身边有人默默陪伴会更容易度过", "timestamp": 1629693234, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2338451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2337138, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我看到戒了药就感到心里一惊\n\n药一定是在医生指导下慢慢来断药啊 不是自己说戒就戒的", "timestamp": 1629693328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2339158, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2338451, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 没有，是当时就有好转医生让减药，后面疫情断药了一小段时间买到了后又接着吃了，后面慢慢减量戒的", "timestamp": 1629699501, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2339775, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 447373, "reply_to": 2339158, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 抱抱dz~~ 我感觉一是定期复诊，遵医嘱服药；二是心理咨询。 抑郁期的时候可能有些话想对朋友说但觉得不合适，或者害怕自己情绪影响到朋友。这个时候每周跟咨询师聊一聊，还挺好的", "timestamp": 1629704840, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 447373, "reply": 12, "tag": null, "text": "怎么坚持活下去啊", "timestamp": 1629656872, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629704842, "url": "", "vote": {}}}